<TITLE> Card fair kicks off Friday </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, May 19 (bdnews24.com)The Bank Card Fair kicks off Friday at the city's Bangabandhu International Convention Centre. The three-day fair, first of its kind, has been organised by a weekly business magazine, the Financial Mirror. bdnews24.com is the web partner of the event. The fair is meant to familiarise people with the concept of credit cards and debit cards, says a statement of the organisers. The organisers expect about 40 companies including leading banks and mobile phone company City Cell to participate in the fair
